{
  "stem": "26576.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It wasn't the triumph that my father thought that-- that will happen.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And it was very sad.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And our-- so beginnings, which was 1945 I remember so really very sad.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Although I tried to make the best for-- of it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But we-- we didn't go to Sosnowiec, but we went to Katowice, which is only a few kilometers away.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Because Katowice was a larger city.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And the city was completely-- there were no Jews.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And we got a house, a flat actual that a German vacated.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And immediately, immediately my father got in contact with New York.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And he started a committee, which was called the Jewish Committee, to help the people.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Because a lot of what was happening, we came to Sosnowiec-- to Katowice, it would be the end of September 1945.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And a lot of young people were coming from the concentration camps back to Poland in search of their families.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Also and that I remember already well at the time, quite a few people that were in hiding like, these people that were in hiding.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Like one of my mother's friends was in hiding from Losice.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And she was telling my mother what happened to the family, what happened to the ghetto, and Siedlce.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "But she survived the war and went to Israel later on.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "But-- but my parents were so terrible upset with everything that happened.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And that they tried to at least to help the young people.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And I remember a lot, a lot of young people coming back from Germany in search of their parents, family.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And of course not many, there were isolated cases where they would find somebody.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "But on the whole, there wasn't many that did find their family.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
